Sentencas: A solid oxide fuel cell based on double-sided cathodes is developed in our group, showing special properties and many advantages under some harsh conditions.
Titulo: 3D thermo-electro-chemo-mechanical coupled modeling of solid oxide fuel cell with double-sided cathodes

Sentencas: To optimize the cell further, a thermo-electro-chemo-mechanical coupled 3D model is developed to simulate the distributions of temperature, current density, fuel gas and thermal stress under different voltages.
Titulo: 3D thermo-electro-chemo-mechanical coupled modeling of solid oxide fuel cell with double-sided cathodes

Sentencas: The numerical results indicate that the temperature distribution, current, fuel gases and thermal stress is non-uniform in the cell at different voltages.
Titulo: 3D thermo-electro-chemo-mechanical coupled modeling of solid oxide fuel cell with double-sided cathodes

Sentencas: The distribution of thermal stress in the electrolyte is also non-uniform because of the un-even electrochemical reaction and convective heat transfer.
Titulo: 3D thermo-electro-chemo-mechanical coupled modeling of solid oxide fuel cell with double-sided cathodes

Sentencas: Furthermore, the result shows that about 47%similar to 54% of maximum 1st principal stress in SOFC is caused by the mismatch of coefficients of thermal expansion (CTEs) among materials, while the other part of the maximum 1st principal stress is mainly caused by temperature gradient.
Titulo: 3D thermo-electro-chemo-mechanical coupled modeling of solid oxide fuel cell with double-sided cathodes
